{"tid":1425551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[召文宣] 要令港豬轉軚支持我哋","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:51:28.000Z","uid":294981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f572c8735c28dff2b8a05fee24d65def5df888ca","tid":1425551,"uid":294981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:40:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>我哋嘅目標唔單只要本來支持我哋嘅人繼續支持我哋，更加要令本來反對我哋嘅人轉軚支持我哋</strong><br />\n好多支持政府嘅港豬都以為逃犯條例唔會影響到佢哋生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n豬只會關心飼料，我哋就同佢討論飼料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHUMAN ARE DRIVEN BY FEAR<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">集思廣益</span> : 究竟港豬怕什麼 / 怕失去什麼?<br />\n-錢?<br />\n-屋企?<br />\n-吃喝玩樂???<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><br />\n我哋要針對佢哋關心嘅嘢進行新一輪文宣!!!!!</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e2f80c1cd34298b019c64ff537529c67bad54f6a","tid":1425551,"uid":294981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:43:28.000Z","msg":"我先!<br />\n港女好似驚冇得返鄉下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxLsyon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxLsyon.jpg&h=77b1919b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df865f55ee3f05692f0739016eb48c76282c35d6","tid":1425551,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:51:28.000Z","msg":"好多嘢要親身體驗過先會有感覺<br />\n多啲約佢哋去會有警察擾民嘅地方行街食飯就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}